cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on improving the performance of multiple object tracking using appearance information and a deep association metric. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the use of deep learning and machine learning algorithms suggests that it could also belong to the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with real-time tracking, which could place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) or robotics (cs.RO) categories.
